Products.RichDescription:
PADDLE POP ICE CONFECTION STRAWBERRY MILKSHAKE 544 ML 8X68ML.

PADDLE POP ICE CREAM STRAWBERRY MILKSHAKE
SAY GOODBYE SERIOUS, HELLO JOY. 10 delicious sticks of Streets Chocolate Paddle Pops for the family to enjoy as dessert or just any time of the day. Made with wholesome dairy milk and contains no artificial colours. Available in a 8 pack it is perfect for friends and family and a real treat for the kids! A refreshing treat for hot days or the perfect snack all the time! Between World War 1 and World War 2, Edwin (‘Ted’) Street with the help of his wife and brother laid the foundations (in Corrimal, NSW) for what would ultimately become Australia’s biggest and best-known ice cream manufacturer. Streets ice cream was originally made in the back shed by Ted Street. He would then sell these to neighbours along with sweets, cakes and lemonade. Popularity grew and he soon used a cart, then a one horse power motorbike to sell Streets ice cream. It continued to grow and today Streets ice cream is sold throughout Australia and New Zealand with well known brands such as Magnum, Viennetta, Paddle Pop, Cornetto, Gaytime, Calippo and Blue Ribbon.
Enjoy the delicious Strawberry Paddlepop Pop taste today!

Made with Australian or New Zealand Dairy

Delicious strawberry milkshake flavour!

Source of calcium & No artificial colours!

Now in an 8 pack!

Enjoy our multipack paddle pops as a tasty treat today!

Made in Australia!

Products.SmallFormatDescription: Weis Sorbet Summer Berries
Products.FullDescription: Weis Sorbet Summer Berries
Products.RichDescription:
WEIS ICE CREAM SORBET BERRY 1 LTR

For a pint-sized fruit, they certainly deliver a complex burst of flavour. That’s why it took us some time to perfect the recipe for our Weis Berry Sorbet. We discovered that the bold raspberries had to be balanced out by just the right amount of sweet strawberries. Then using a traditional sorbet recipe, we blended the berries together to create a light, refreshing dessert. You’ll be pleased to know these berry beauties are delivered to our factory whole so we can inspect their quality and ensure they’re at their flavour peak. This way we can guarantee you the berry, berry best in every tub. Our delicously refreshing sorbet range is sure to be a hit in any home, particularly over the warmer summer months! Weis Sorbets are dairy free, made with real fruit, and have no artificial colours or flavours. Even better, they are absolutely delicious. Our classic sorbet flavours, like Australian Mango, Summer Berries and Refreshing Lemon, are a delightful and refreshing treat, great for after dinner or as a summertime snack. Or, if you are looking for something a little different, we now have a range of exotic sorbets. Weis Sorbet Exotics are sorbets with a twist! They are packed with interesting fruit and flavour combinations to create a truly surprising sorbet sensation!

Our Summer Berries Sorbet is made with real fruit

A complex mix of tangy raspberry and sweet strawberry creating a smooth sorbet texture.

Dairy and gluten free

99% fat free and vegan friendly

A refreshing alternative to ice cream

Made in Australia since 1957
